body:
(From API review)

Is this still required after https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/pull/15132 ? Once that PR is merged, then it seems like the behavior of this PR will be the same as connecting the existing `TextLineReader` op to the output of a `DecodeCompressed` op?

Are we missing something?
